A browser-based generative music tool that learns from MIDI files and creates new melodies. Built with Svelte 5, Tone.js, and a bigram probability model running entirely in the browser.

MIDI Files → Notes → Patterns → Tokens → Model → Generation → Music
(raw)       (clean) (examples) (input) (learning) (output) (audio)

```bash
ai-music-sandbox/
├── web/
│ ├── src/
│ │ ├── lib/
│ │ │ ├── music/ # Core ML logic
│ │ │ │ ├── bigram.ts # Bigram probability model
│ │ │ │ ├── midiConverter.ts 
│ │ │ │ ├── generation.ts # Generation store & logic
│ │ │ │ └── model.json # Trained model data
│ │ │ └── stores/ # Svelte stores
│ │ └── routes/
│ └── static/ # Generated MIDI files
│
├── dataset/ # Training MIDI files
│ ├── bach/
│ ├── liszt/
│ └── ...
│
└── data/ 
└── models/ 

```

Run it with

```bash
cd web
yarn install
yarn run dev
```
